# Repository-specific .gitignore for notoriousjayy-rename
#
# Notes:
# - This repo intentionally tracks many generated-looking source files
#   (for example cweb/common.c, cweb/ctangle.c, and numerous graphbase/*.c).
#   Do NOT add broad rules like *.c or *.h.
# - It also tracks historical/project files such as .w, .ch, .tex, .dat,
#   .correct, .dsp, and .dsw. Those are kept out of ignore rules on purpose.

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
\#*\#
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Generic native build outputs ---
*.o
*.obj
*.lo
*.la
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.so.*
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.pdb
